column5: Sad to say once again people have run after the pool is over. We only had 5 people pay up so far.  If you have forgot about it plase PM me and I will let you know where to send the 25 bucks next season we will be collecting before hand...

No surprise.  I almost got executed for suggesting that people join a free Fantasy Fishing Pool.  Who could ever imagine that people on a fishing site would be interested in fantasy fishing!  Better luck next year.
such a shame...  I guess people are just upset that a woman won first place!
You might have called it the "OFC football pool" Jamie, but it had nothing whatsoever to do with OFC. I just want to make that perfectly clear.
Amen Roy...  thought guys here would like to play ( and pay)...  did not even name it OFC this year...
